                            Tales of the Automaton: The Big Birdocalypse
                        </div>
                    

                    
                        <div id="breadcrumbs">
                            <a href="/foundation-tales">Tales Hub</a> &raquo; <a href="/series-archive">Series Archive</a> &raquo; <a href="/bird">Team Bird Hub</a> &raquo; Tales of the Automaton: The Big Birdocalypse
